hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Could you ask him to call me? hghmeds.com feedback In this bold look Kimberley Walsh is certainly having a statement day. Teamed with the yellow jumper, she has managed to hit a whole host of this season's top trends: pastels, pencil skirts and prints. What's more, this wild pattern can be matched or clashed with a whole host of other hues depending on your taste. Team with a simple black jumper and slippers for a chic take on evening dressing.
